018/**
019 * DTO for an HTML <a class="doclink" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/document-metadata.html#the-meta-element">&lt;meta&gt;</a>
020 * element.
021 *
022 * <ul class='seealso'>
023 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="../../../../../overview-summary.html#juneau-dto.jd.Html5">Overview &gt; juneau-dto &gt; HTML5</a>
024 * </ul>
025 */
026@Bean(typeName="meta")
027@FluentSetters
028public class Meta extends HtmlElementVoid {
029
030   /**
031    * Creates an empty {@link Meta} element.
032    */
033   public Meta() {}
034
035   /**
036    * <a class="doclink" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/document-metadata.html#attr-meta-charset">charset</a>
037    * attribute.
038    *
039    * <p>
040    * Character encoding declaration.
041    *
042    * @param charset The new value for this attribute.
043    * @return This object.
044    */
045   public final Meta charset(String charset) {
046      attr("charset", charset);
047      return this;
048   }
049
050   /**
051    * <a class="doclink" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/document-metadata.html#attr-meta-content">content</a>
052    * attribute.
053    *
054    * <p>
055    * Value of the element.
056    *
057    * @param content The new value for this attribute.
058    * @return This object.
059    */
060   public final Meta content(String content) {
061      attr("content", content);
062      return this;
063   }
064
065   /**
066    * <a class="doclink" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/document-metadata.html#attr-meta-http-equiv">http-equiv</a>
067    * attribute.
068    *
069    * <p>
070    * Pragma directive.
071    *
072    * @param httpequiv The new value for this attribute.
073    * @return This object.
074    */
075   public final Meta httpequiv(String httpequiv) {
076      attr("http-equiv", httpequiv);
077      return this;
078   }
079
080   /**
081    * <a class="doclink" href="https://www.w3.org/TR/html5/document-metadata.html#attr-meta-name">name</a> attribute.
082    *
083    * <p>
084    * Metadata name.
085    *
086    * @param name The new value for this attribute.
087    * @return This object.
088    */
089   public final Meta name(String name) {
090      attr("name", name);
091      return this;
092   }
